  <summary date="2021-03-17T18:40:27Z" status="Introduced in House">Water Power Research and Development Act 

This bill directs the Department of Energy (DOE) to carry out programs of research, development, demonstration, and commercial application for water power technologies, hydropower, and marine energy technologies. Additionally, DOE must award grants to institutions of higher education for the continuation and expansion of research and development at the National Marine Energy Centers and the establishments of new centers.</summary>
